snippet.title: Skully Bunnies the Mobile Game
snippet.description: Skully Bunnies is a fast paced, competitive, party card game. To win the game, a player must be the first to fuse 3 Skully Bunnies together. Strategy fused with luck of the draw creates intense gameplay. The fun factor to this game is not only unique, but highly contagious. Skully Bunnies mobile card game creates new fast paced action mixed like never before.
